ves you a home and lifestyle e-commerce store that looks editorial and high-end, and you don't need design skills or developer help to make it work. The warm Scandinavian aesthetic—terracotta accents, cream backgrounds, serif typography—sets a tone that makes artisan products feel worth their price.\n\nThe technical parts are already handled. A complete shopping flow from browsing to checkout, persistent cart and wishlist, mobile-responsive layouts, collection filtering via URL parameters, and product sorting with five options—all built in. You can focus on curating your products and building a brand people remember.\n\nEvery detail is designed to make your store feel premium—not like a DIY project. The sharp editorial aesthetic, smooth scrolling effects, and polished product interactions give customers the impression they're shopping a high-end brand. This template doesn't look like a template—it looks like something a creative director built for you.\n\n## Who This Is For\n\n- Home goods makers and artisans launching their first online store without a developer budget\n- Lifestyle brand founders who need their site to match the quality of what they sell\n- Boutique owners moving from marketplaces to a standalone store they actually control\n- Interior designers and stylists showcasing curated product collections alongside their work\n- Agency teams building polished e-commerce sites for home and lifestyle clients on tight timelines\n- Small batch producers who want presentation that justifies premium pricing\n\n## Best Use Cases\n\n### Artisan Home Goods Stores\nSell handmade ceramics, textiles, candles, or furniture with a storefront that feels as considered as your craft. The editorial layout with asymmetric collection grids and rich product detail pages—including materials, dimensions, and multiple image views—gives each piece the presentation it deserves.\n\n### Curated Lifestyle Boutiques\nBuild a multi-collection store around a lifestyle point of view. Customers can browse eight collections, filter by category, and sort by price, popularity, or what's new—all on a page that looks editorial and works smoothly on any device. The cohesive typography and warm color palette keep your brand feeling polished everywhere.\n\n### Brand Launch and Market Entry\nGet a professional storefront running before your first product drops. The complete shopping flow—from browsing and wishlisting through cart and checkout—means you're not just showing products, you're ready to take orders. Persistent cart state means customers can come back and finish what they started.\n\n### Client Projects for Lifestyle Brands\nPresent clients with a working store instead of a static mockup. The smooth animations, polished hover effects, and fully interactive shopping flow—browsing, filtering, cart, and checkout—demonstrate the kind of quality that wins project approvals. Every interaction feels intentional, making it easy to get client sign-off.\n\n## Getting Started\n\n### Step 1: Remix This Template\n\nClick \"Remix\" to create your copy. You'll have a complete home and lifestyle store ready to customize—twelve products across eight collections, a full shopping cart, wishlist functionality, and a checkout flow. All the pages and features are already working—you just need to make it yours.\n\n### Step 2: Customize Your Brand\n\nMake the design yours. Swap the terracotta and cream palette for your brand colors, choose different fonts, and adjust layouts to match your style. The sharp, editorial design language adapts to different brand identities without losing its polish. You don't need to know code to make it look exactly how you want.\n\n### Step 3: Add Your Content\n\nReplace the sample products with your own inventory—upload your product photography and write descriptions that tell the story behind each piece, then add material and dimension details. Organize items into collections that make sense for your brand, with filtering and discovery tools built to highlight what matters. The product gallery features smooth image transitions, a thumbnail strip for easy navigation, and elegant controls that make every product page feel editorial. The template stays out of your way—your products stay the focus.\n\n### Step 4: Connect Your Tools\n\nThe checkout form and cart system are structured and ready for backend connections. Lovable has built-in integrations for the tools e-commerce businesses actually use—link payment processing for real transactions, connect email marketing to capture newsletter subscribers, and add analytics to track performance as you scale.\n\n### Step 5: Go Live\n\nDeploy your store with one click. Lovable handles the hosting, security, and performance optimization automatically. Share your storefront link and start selling—your store goes live worldwide in minutes.\n\n## Conclusion\n\nThis home and lifestyle store template works for makers and brand founders who want their online presence to match the quality of what they create. You get editorial-grade design without hiring a creative agency, a complete shopping experience with filtering, sorting, cart, and checkout features without building it from scratch, and the kind of visual polish that makes customers trust your brand—all without writing a line of code.\n\nWhether you're launching your first standalone store or moving away from a marketplace that limits your brand, this template gives you a solid foundation. The product galleries display beautifully, collection filtering works smoothly on every screen size, and the cart persists between visits so customers don't lose what they've picked. Choose this template to launch a storefront that looks intentional and grows with your catalog."])</script><script nonce="IL1bsFwmQsw8QNMKGKtJNQ==">self.__next_f.push([1,"4c:Teaa,"])</script><script nonce="IL1bsFwmQsw8QNMKGKtJNQ==">self.__next_f.push([1,"\nThis template gives you a visual mood board tool built around a spatial canvas. Upload images, arrange them freely, add text notes, and generate new images with AI — all on a zoomable, pannable workspace with a dot grid background.\n\nEach board is a separate canvas where you can place items at any position and size. Drag to reposition, use corner handles to resize or rotate, and right-click for context actions like copy, paste, and delete. Everything saves automatically to the database.\n\nThe dashboard lets you create, rename, reorder, and delete boards. Each board shows a thumbnail preview and timestamp. Boards can be reordered with drag-and-drop.\n\nAuthentication is built in — users sign up with email (or Google), verify their account, and get access to their private boards. All data is scoped to the authenticated user.\n\n## Who This Is For\n\nDesigners collecting visual references and building mood boards for client projects\n\nArt directors organizing inspiration across campaigns and brand directions\n\nContent creators planning visual themes for social media or editorial work\n\nCreative teams collaborating on visual direction in a shared workspace\n\nAnyone who thinks visually and wants a better way to collect and arrange inspiration\n\n## Best Use Cases\n\n### Brand and Campaign Mood Boards\n\nCollect visual references for a new brand identity or campaign. Arrange images spatially to see how colors, textures, and styles relate to each other. Add text notes to capture thoughts alongside the visuals.\n\n### Design Project References\n\nBuild a reference board before starting a design project. Upload screenshots, photos, and illustrations. Use AI generation to explore visual directions you haven't found yet.\n\n### Content Planning\n\nPlan visual themes for social media, editorial shoots, or product launches. Organize images by mood, palette, or concept across separate boards.\n\n### Personal Inspiration Archive\n\nKeep a running collection of things that catch your eye. Create boards by topic — architecture, typography, fashion, interiors — and revisit them whenever you need a creative spark.\n\n## Getting Started\n\n### Step 1: Remix This Template\n\nClick \"Remix\" to create your copy. You'll have a working mood board app you can explore before adding your own content.\n\n### Step 2: Familiarize Yourself With the Project\n\nGo to User \u003e Settings \u003e Knowledge, and read what's under \"Project knowledge\" to understand the intended architecture and data model. You can also ask Lovable in the chat for more details.\n\n### Step 3: Customize Your Brand\n\nUpdate colors, fonts, and your app name. The design system uses semantic tokens so you can change the entire look by editing a few CSS variables.\n\n### Step 4: Create Your First Board\n\nSign up, head to the dashboard, and create a new board. Upload images, add text, and arrange everything on the canvas.\n\n### Step 5: Try AI Image Generation\n\nUse the magic wand tool in the floating dock to generate images from text prompts directly onto your canvas.\n\n### Step 6: Go Live\n\nDeploy with one click and share with your team. Lovable handles hosting and performance.\n\n### Step 7: Iterate and Make It Yours\n\nContinue building and make any changes to the app to suit your creative workflow and preferences.\n\n## Conclusion\n\nThis mood board creator works for designers, art directors, content creators, and anyone who thinks visually. You get an infinite canvas, drag-and-drop image management, AI generation, text annotations, and multi-board organization in a template you can deploy in minutes. Whether you're planning a brand direction, collecting references for a project, or building a visual archive, the spatial layout replaces the Pinterest board or folder of screenshots you've been juggling.\n"])</script><script nonce="IL1bsFwmQsw8QNMKGKtJNQ==">self.__next_f.push([1,"4d:Td1a,"])</script><script nonce="IL1bsFwmQsw8QNMKGKtJNQ==">self.__next_f.push([1,"This template gives you a newsletter site that looks professional and you don't need design skills to make it work.\n\nThe technical parts are already handled. Mobile responsiveness, fast loading, email signup forms—all done. You can focus on creating content your readers want to see.\n\n## **Who This Is For**\n\n- Writers and journalists building independent publications\n- Industry experts sharing insights and analysis with their audience\n- Creators monetizing through paid subscriptions and sponsorships\n- Thought leaders establishing authority in their field\n- Companies and brands running content marketing newsletters\n- Podcasters and video creators adding written content to their offering\n\n## **Best Use Cases**\n\n**Independent Publishing**: Launch your own publication without platform fees eating into your revenue. You own the subscriber list and control how you monetize your writing.\n\n**Industry Commentary**: Share weekly or monthly analysis about your industry. The clean layout keeps readers focused on your insights instead of fighting with cluttered design.\n\n**Curated Digests**: Compile the best articles, resources, and links in your niche. Readers subscribe because you save them time finding what matters, and the template makes curation look effortless.\n\n**Personal Thought Leadership**: Build your reputation by consistently sharing valuable perspectives. The professional presentation signals credibility before readers even start reading your content.\n\n## **Getting Started**\n\n**Step 1: Remix This Template**\n\nClick \"Remix\" to create your copy. You'll have a complete newsletter site ready to customize. All the pages and features are already working—you just need to make it yours.\n\n**Step 2: Customize Your Brand**\n\nChange colors to match your aesthetic. Update fonts to reflect your style. Lovable's visual editor lets you modify layouts and see changes instantly as you work. You don't need to know code to make it look exactly how you want.\n\n**Step 3: Add Your Content**\n\nReplace the sample issues with your writing, analysis, and commentary. Upload your author photo and write a bio that connects with your target audience. The template stays out of your way so your content is what people notice.\n\n**Step 4: Connect Your Tools**\n\nIntegrate email service providers like Supabase for subscriber management, connect Stripe for paid subscriptions, or add analytics to track which topics resonate. Lovable has built-in integrations for the tools newsletter publishers actually use.\n\n**Step 5: Go Live**\n\nDeploy your newsletter site with one click. Lovable handles the hosting, security, and performance optimization automatically. Your publication goes live worldwide in minutes, and you can start building your subscriber list.\n\n## **Conclusion**\n\nThis newsletter template works for creators who want their publication to look as polished as their writing. You get professional design without hiring a developer and fast performance without technical optimization. Whether you're starting your first newsletter or moving from a platform that takes a cut of your revenue, this template gives you a solid foundation. The signup forms work properly, mobile reading experience is smooth, and everything loads fast from day one. Choose this template to launch a newsletter that represents your voice and grows with your audience.\n"])</script><script nonce="IL1bsFwmQsw8QNMKGKtJNQ==">self.__next_f.push([1,"4e:Tcc4,"])</script><script nonce="IL1bsFwmQsw8QNMKGKtJNQ==">self.__next_f.push([1,"This template gives you a fashion blog that looks professional and you don't need design skills to make it work.\n\nThe technical parts are already handled. Mobile responsiveness, fast loading, SEO setup—all done. You can focus on creating content your readers want to see.\n\n## **Who This Is For**\n\n- Fashion bloggers building their personal brand and online presence\n- Style influencers who need professional layouts for outfit posts and lookbooks\n- Personal stylists showcasing their work and attracting new clients\n- Boutique owners combining blog content with product features\n- Lifestyle creators covering fashion, beauty, and trends\n\n## **Best Use Cases**\n\n**Personal Style Blogs**: Document your daily outfits, seasonal wardrobes, and fashion experiments. The layouts work well for visual storytelling, which is what personal style content needs.\n\n**Fashion Reviews**: Review clothing brands, test sustainable fashion, and share honest product opinions. Readers who trust your taste will come back for your recommendations.\n\n**Trend Analysis**: Cover runway shows, street style, and emerging trends. The professional layouts help establish you as someone who knows what they're talking about in the industry.\n\n**Styling Services**: Show before-and-after transformations and share client success stories. The portfolio-quality presentation helps you attract new styling clients who want to see proof of your work.\n\n## **Getting Started**\n\n**Step 1: Remix This Template**\n\nClick \"Remix\" to create your copy. You'll have a complete fashion blog ready to customize. All the pages and features are already working—you just need to make it yours.\n\n**Step 2: Customize Your Brand**\n\nChange colors to match your aesthetic. Update fonts to reflect your style. Lovable's visual editor lets you modify layouts and see changes instantly as you work. You don't need to know code to make it look exactly how you want.\n\n**Step 3: Add Your Content**\n\nReplace the sample posts with your outfit photos, styling tips, and fashion commentary. Upload your best images and write captions that connect with your audience. The template stays out of your way so your content is what people notice.\n\n**Step 4: Connect Your Tools**\n\nLink your Instagram feed, connect email marketing through Supabase, add Google Analytics, or integrate affiliate platforms. Lovable has built-in integrations for the tools fashion bloggers actually use.\n\n**Step 5: Go Live**\n\nDeploy your fashion blog with one click. Lovable handles the hosting, security, and performance optimization automatically. Your blog goes live worldwide in minutes, and you can start sharing the URL with your audience.\n\n## **Conclusion**\n\nThis fashion blog template works for creators who want their site to look as polished as their content. You get professional design without hiring a developer, fast performance without technical optimization, and all the features fashion bloggers actually use. Whether you're starting your first blog or upgrading from a basic platform, this template gives you a solid foundation. The image galleries work properly, mobile navigation is smooth, and everything loads fast from day one. Choose this template to launch a fashion blog that represents your style and grows with your audience.\n"])</script><script nonce="IL1bsFwmQsw8QNMKGKtJNQ==">self.__next_f.push([1,"4f:Tf0b,"])</script><script nonce="IL1bsFwmQsw8QNMKGKtJNQ==">self.__next_f.push([1,"\nContinuum is a minimalist habit tracker designed to help users build and maintain consistent daily routines. It strips away the noise of bloated habit apps and focuses on what matters: logging habits, watching streaks grow, and staying accountable to yourself.\n\nEach habit includes a name, description, color, frequency schedule, and optional reminder time. Check off habits daily, track your current and longest streaks, and visualize your consistency with a 30-day calendar heatmap. Milestone messages celebrate your progress at key intervals like 7, 30, and 365 days.\n\nThe app supports flexible scheduling — daily, specific weekdays, or a target number of times per week. Drag-and-drop reordering lets you prioritize what matters most. All data syncs to the cloud via authentication, so your habits follow you across devices.\n\nAuthentication is built in with email/password signup and Google sign-in. A clean onboarding flow guides new users through creating their first habits. The settings page lets you manage your account and clear data when needed.\n\n## Who This Is For\n\nIndividuals building daily routines who want a simple, distraction-free tracker\n\nSelf-improvement enthusiasts who are motivated by streaks and visual progress\n\nPeople frustrated with bloated habit apps full of social features and ads\n\nDevelopers looking for a clean habit tracker template to customize and extend\n\n## Best Use Cases\n\n### Daily Routine Building\n\nTrack morning routines, exercise habits, reading goals, or meditation practice. The daily check-off flow is fast and satisfying, and streak counters provide the motivation to keep going. No distractions, just you and your habits.\n\n### Flexible Weekly Goals\n\nNot every habit needs to happen daily. Set habits for specific weekdays or target a number of completions per week. The scheduling system adapts to your real life instead of forcing a rigid daily cadence.\n\n### Personal Accountability\n\nThe calendar heatmap and streak milestones create a visual record of your consistency. Seeing a long streak or a filled-in heatmap makes it harder to skip a day. It's accountability without the social pressure.\n\n### Progress Tracking Over Time\n\nUse the insights page to review completion rates, compare streaks across habits, and identify patterns. The analytics help you understand which habits stick and which ones need adjustment.\n\n## Getting Started\n\n### Step 1: Remix This Template\n\nClick \"Remix\" to create your copy. You'll have a working habit tracker you can explore before adding your own customizations.\n\n### Step 2: Familiarize Yourself With the Project\n\nGo to User \u003e Settings \u003e Knowledge, and read what's under \"Project knowledge\" to understand the app's architecture and data model. You can also ask Lovable in the chat for more details.\n\n### Step 3: Customize Your Brand\n\nUpdate colors, fonts, and the app name. The design system uses CSS custom properties and Tailwind tokens, so changes propagate instantly across the entire app.\n\n### Step 4: Try the Habit Tracking Flow\n\nCreate a few habits, check them off, and explore the insights page to see streaks, completion rates, and the calendar heatmap in action.\n\n### Step 5: Deploy and Start Tracking\n\nDeploy with one click and start building your daily routine. Lovable handles hosting and performance.\n\n### Step 6: Iterate and Make It Yours\n\nContinue building and make any changes to suit your exact preferences and workflow.\n\n## Conclusion\n\nContinuum works for anyone who wants a focused, personal habit tracker without social pressure or premium paywalls. You get streak tracking, calendar heatmaps, flexible scheduling, drag-and-drop reordering, and cloud sync in a template you can deploy in minutes. Whether you're building a morning routine or tracking fitness goals, the clean interface keeps you focused on consistency rather than complexity.\n"])</script><script nonce="IL1bsFwmQsw8QNMKGKtJNQ==">self.__next_f.push([1,"50:T7a5,"])</script><script nonce="IL1bsFwmQsw8QNMKGKtJNQ==">self.__next_f.push([1,"\nBuild presentations that go beyond static slides. Combine the familiarity of traditional slide decks with the power of code and interactive web components.\n\n## Perfect For\n\n- **Product Demos**: Show live features with interactive components and real-time data\n- **Business Pitches**: Dynamic charts, calculations, and data visualizations\n- **Educational Content**: Interactive learning with simulations and explorable examples\n- **Technical Showcases**: Complex visualizations, 3D graphics, and custom interactions\n- **Conference Talks**: Engaging presentations with live coding examples and demos\n\n## Key Capabilities\n\n**Code-Powered Flexibility** - Build anything you can create with React. Add custom components, interactive charts, data visualizations, forms, animations, or any web technology.\n\n**Real-Time Interactivity** - Create presentations where users can manipulate parameters, adjust values, and see results update live. Perfect for demos and educational content.\n\n**No Limitations** - Unlike PowerPoint or Google Slides, you have complete control. Use any npm package, connect to APIs, or build custom interactions tailored to your needs.\n\n**Professional Delivery** - Beautiful gradients, modern design system, fullscreen presentation mode, and keyboard navigation for polished presentations.\n\n## Technical Features\n\n- Fixed 1920x1080 resolution with automatic scaling\n- Sidebar thumbnail navigation\n- Fullscreen presentation mode with keyboard controls\n- Progress indicators and zoom controls\n- Mobile-responsive layouts\n- Keyboard navigation (arrow keys, Space, Escape)\n\n## Use This Template\n\nStart with 6 pre-built example slides showing what's possible:\n1. Title slide with gradient background\n2. Interactive charts and simulations\n3. Real-time calculations and metrics\n4. 3D object viewer\n5. Custom interactive components\n6. Call-to-action slide\n\nCustomize everything—colors, content, interactions, and components to match your needs.\n"])</script><script nonce="IL1bsFwmQsw8QNMKGKtJNQ==">self.__next_f.push([1,"51:T1698,"])</script><script nonce="IL1bsFwmQsw8QNMKGKtJNQ==">self.__next_f.push([1,"This template gives you a portfolio that looks professional and you don't need design skills to make it work. The layouts are built for showcasing creative work—photography, design projects, client deliverables, or service offerings—with the kind of presentation quality that justifies premium rates.\n\nYour portfolio works beautifully on any device clients use to view it—desktop, tablet, or mobile. Projects reveal themselves with subtle interactions that keep attention on your work. You can switch between light and dark modes to match your aesthetic, and organize projects by category so clients quickly find relevant examples. You can focus on selecting your best projects while the template handles professional presentation.\n\nThe design system is already polished and professional, so you don't have to hire a designer or spend weeks tweaking layouts. Every interaction—from the parallax effects to the image transitions—is designed to keep attention on your work. You focus on selecting your best projects while the template handles the presentation quality that justifies premium pricing.\n\n## Who This Is For\n\n- Freelance photographers and designers showcasing client work to justify premium rates\n- Service providers building professional portfolios to compete with established agencies\n- Creative consultants displaying client deliverables to build trust with prospects\n- Design agencies presenting client work to win competitive pitches\n- Independent artists and illustrators showcasing creative work without learning to code\n- Brand strategists and visual designers demonstrating aesthetic judgment through portfolio presentation\n\n## Best Use Cases\n\n**Client Work Showcases**: Show clients exactly what they need to see: your best work organized by project type, with clear descriptions of the problems you solved and the results you delivered. Each project displays with professional image layouts that make your work look worth premium rates. The professional presentation keeps attention focused on your work quality rather than the website itself.\n\n**Service Portfolio Presentations**: Display the range of services you offer through visual examples of your best work. The category system lets you organize projects by service type, industry, or skill set. Potential clients can quickly see if you've solved problems similar to theirs, which builds trust faster than generic service descriptions.\n\n**Agency Pitch Materials**: Showcase client work with professionally designed layouts that emphasize visual impact. The interactive project displays and responsive project detail pages create presentations that stand out from template-based competitors. Walk prospects through your portfolio with interactive hover states and a clean design system that demonstrates professional polish and differentiation.\n\n**Professional Brand Building**: Establish yourself as someone who takes their work seriously through presentation quality that matches your expertise. The clean typography, sophisticated interactions, and attention to detail signal that you're established and professional. This matters when you're competing for clients who have multiple options and judge quality quickly.\n\n## Getting Started\n\n### Step 1: Remix This Template\n\nClick \"Remix\" to create your copy. You'll have a complete portfolio site ready to customize. All the pages, project layouts, and interactive features are already working—you just need to make it yours and add your actual work.\n\n### Step 2: Customize Your Brand\n\nChange colors to match your brand aesthetic. The template comes with dark and light modes you can customize. Update fonts to reflect your style. Lovable's visual editor lets you modify layouts and see changes instantly as you work. You don't need to know code to make it look exactly how you want.\n\n### Step 3: Add Your Content\n\nReplace the sample projects with your actual client work and portfolio pieces. Upload your best images and write descriptions that explain your process, the client's challenge, and the results you delivered. The template stays out of your way so your work is what people notice. Use the category system to organize projects by type (Photography, Digital Art, Fine Art).\n\n### Step 4: Connect Your Tools\n\nLink your Instagram or Behance feed to showcase recent work, connect email marketing tools to capture leads, add Google Analytics to track portfolio views, or integrate scheduling tools for client consultations. Lovable has built-in integrations for the tools creative professionals actually use.\n\n### Step 5: Go Live\n\nDeploy your portfolio with one click. Lovable handles the hosting, security, and performance optimization automatically. Your portfolio goes live worldwide in minutes with responsive layouts that work beautifully on all devices, and you can start sharing the URL with clients and prospects immediately.\n\n## Conclusion\n\nThis portfolio template works for creative professionals and service providers who want a modern showcase for their work without hiring a developer. You get professional design without technical complexity, polished interactions without coding, and organized project showcases without custom development. The template includes responsive layouts, professional typography, and light and dark modes—plus all the project organization features you need to compete for higher-value clients.\n\nWhether you're building your first portfolio to attract clients or upgrading from a basic platform that makes you look generic, this template gives you a solid foundation. The presentation quality signals professionalism to clients who judge expertise quickly. Choose this template to launch a portfolio that differentiates you from competitors and attracts clients willing to pay for quality work.\n"])</script><script nonce="IL1bsFwmQsw8QNMKGKtJNQ==">self.__next_f.push([1,"52:Tde7,"])</script><script nonce="IL1bsFwmQsw8QNMKGKtJNQ==">self.__next_f.push([1,"This template gives you a complete e-commerce store that looks polished without requiring design skills or technical setup. Product pages, checkout flows, mobile layouts, and cart functionality are already in place.\n\nEverything works on every device. Customers can browse, zoom in on details, add items to their cart, and check out smoothly without you configuring layouts or handling complex storefront logic. Your focus stays on adding products and preparing for sales instead of troubleshooting an online store.\n\nThe minimalist luxury presentation avoids the generic appearance common in off-the-shelf builders. The layouts keep attention on your products and support premium positioning.\n\n## Who This Is For\n\n- Solopreneurs launching product lines and testing demand without developer expense\n\n- Small business owners needing a professional store that supports higher price points\n\n- Agencies delivering client storefronts on tight timelines without draining project resources\n\n- Product sellers exploring new distribution channels or direct-to-consumer sales\n\n- Entrepreneurs creating lifestyle brands who need a storefront that elevates product perception\n\n## Best Use Cases\n\n**Luxury Product Retail**: Sell premium goods with presentation that strengthens perceived quality. Customers see detail and craftsmanship clearly, which reinforces the value of higher-end items.\n\n**Multi-Category Stores**: Organize products across clean, intuitive categories so shoppers can move through your catalog quickly. Finding specific items feels simple, even with larger inventories.\n\n**Artisan and Maker Shops**: Showcase handcrafted work with space for brand storytelling. The template supports pages for your origin story, sustainability notes, care instructions, and store locations. This structure helps customers connect with the value behind your products.\n\n**Direct-to-Consumer Launches**: Launch fast and validate demand immediately. Highlight key products, surface recommendations that lift order values, and start processing real orders without a long development cycle.\n\n## Getting Started\n\n### Step 1: Remix This Template\n\nClick Remix to create your version. All pages and core commerce features are active the moment your copy is generated.\n\n### Step 2: Customize Your Brand\n\nAdjust colors, typography, and layout details through the visual editor. Changes appear instantly, and you never need to handle code. Your store looks aligned with your brand from the start.\n\n### Step 3: Add Your Products\n\nUpload your catalog, add high-quality images, and write clear product descriptions. The layout keeps attention on your products instead of the interface.\n\n### Step 4: Connect Your Tools\n\nAdd your payment provider, set up order notifications, and connect any supporting tools you use. Stripe and other standard integrations work out of the box.\n\n### Step 5: Go Live\n\nDeploy your store with one click. Hosting, performance, and security are handled for you so you can start sharing your store and serving customers immediately.\n\n## Conclusion\n\nThis e-commerce template is shaped for product sellers who want a clean, credible storefront without technical barriers. The structure supports premium branding, the checkout flow is ready from the moment you remix, and the browsing experience stays fast and consistent on every device. It lets you focus on products, customers, and early sales while the platform handles the rest.\n\nChoose this template to launch a store that reflects your brand quality and converts first-time browsers into paying customers.\n"])</script><script nonce="IL1bsFwmQsw8QNMKGKtJNQ==">self.__next_f.push([1,"23:[[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"nonce\":\"IL1bsFwmQsw8QNMKGKtJNQ==\",\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"{\\\"@context\\\":\\\"https://schema.org\\\",\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Organization\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Lovable\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://lovable.dev\\\",\\\"logo\\\":\\\"https://lovable.dev/favicon-192x192.png\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Lovable is your superhuman full stack engineer. Chat with AI to build web apps. Sync with GitHub. One-click deploy.\\\",\\\"sameAs\\\":[\\\"https://twitter.com/lovable\\\",\\\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/lovable-dev\\\",\\\"https://www.youtube.com/@lovable\\\",\\\"https://github.com/lovablelabs\\\"],\\\"foundingDate\\\":\\\"2023\\\",\\\"contactPoint\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ContactPoint\\\",\\\"contactType\\\":\\\"Customer Support\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://lovable.dev/support\\\"}}\"}}],[\"$\",\"$L4a\",null,{\"templates\":[{\"slug\":\"maison-artisan-home-lifestyle-store-template\",\"id\":\"maison-artisan-home-lifestyle-store-template\",\"title\":\"Maison\",\"pageTitle\":\"Maison — Artisan Home \u0026 Lifestyle Store Template\",\"category\":\"Websites\",\"project_id\":\"fc05df19-6b73-4710-b187-5ab806e975ed\",\"url\":\"https://scandi-haven-shop.lovable.app\",\"subtitle\":\"Editorial home goods storefront\",\"description\":\"Launch your artisan home goods store with editorial-grade design that justifies premium pricing. Complete shopping experience with cart, wishlist, and checkout—no developer needed.\",\"metaTitle\":\"Artisan Home \u0026 Lifestyle Store Template | Lovable\",\"metaDescription\":\"Launch a premium home goods store without developers. Editorial design, complete shopping flow, and polished pages that justify artisan pricing.\",\"subcategory\":\"ecommerce\",\"platform\":\"web\",\"screenshot\":\"https://assets.lovable.dev/templates/maison-artisan-home-lifestyle-store-template-screenshot.webp\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://assets.lovable.dev/templates/maison-artisan-home-lifestyle-store-template-screenshot.webp\",\"previewScreenshot\":\"https://assets.lovable.dev/templates/previews/maison-artisan-home-lifestyle-store-template-preview.webp\",\"author\":{\"username\":\"Lovable\",\"avatar\":\"https://lovable.dev/img/logo/lovable-icon-bg-light.png\"},\"featured\":true,\"shownOn\":[\"homepage\",\"dashboard-templates\",\"templates\"],\"date\":\"2026-02-21T09:26:47.665070\",\"lastModified\":\"2026-02-21T09:26:47.665077\",\"highlights\":[{\"icon\":\"palette\",\"title\":\"Editorial-Grade Visual Design\",\"description\":\"Warm Scandinavian aesthetics with parallax effects and smooth animations that make products feel premium.\"},{\"icon\":\"check_circle\",\"title\":\"Complete Shopping Experience\",\"description\":\"Full browse-to-checkout flow with persistent cart and wishlist ready to take orders.\"},{\"icon\":\"cart\",\"title\":\"Professional Product Presentation\",\"description\":\"Multi-image galleries with smooth transitions and detailed material specs for every piece.\"},{\"icon\":\"devices\",\"title\":\"Mobile-First Responsive Layouts\",\"description\":\"Polished shopping experience across all devices with animated menus and touch-friendly filters.\"},{\"icon\":\"code\",\"title\":\"Zero Backend Required\",\"description\":\"Persistent cart and wishlist with local storage so you can launch without developer setup.\"}],\"features\":[{\"title\":\"Parallax Hero Sections\",\"description\":\"Scroll-responsive hero images with Ken Burns animation and content fade effects that create an immersive editorial landing experience.\"},{\"title\":\"Dual-Image Product Cards\",\"description\":\"Hover-triggered image swaps with smooth crossfade transitions show products from multiple angles without requiring clicks.\"},{\"title\":\"Collection Filtering System\",\"description\":\"URL-based filtering with horizontal scrollable category bar and five sorting options lets customers find exactly what they want.\"},{\"title\":\"Rich Product Galleries\",\"description\":\"Carousel with thumbnail strip, prev/next navigation, and crossfade transitions gives each product the presentation it deserves.\"},{\"title\":\"Persistent Cart and Wishlist\",\"description\":\"Zustand-powered state management saves customer selections between visits so they can return and complete purchases.\"},{\"title\":\"Curated Typography Pairing\",\"description\":\"Cormorant Garamond serif headings with Inter sans-serif body create a refined editorial hierarchy from hero to micro-labels.\"},{\"title\":\"Scroll-Triggered Animations\",\"description\":\"Staggered product reveals and collection card animations add polish and movement that makes browsing feel intentional.\"},{\"title\":\"Sticky Product Information\",\"description\":\"Product details and order summary panels stay visible while scrolling, keeping key information accessible during decision-making.\"},{\"title\":\"Complete Checkout Flow\",\"description\":\"Nine-field checkout form with validation ready for backend connection so you can take orders immediately after launch.\"},{\"title\":\"Asymmetric Collection Grids\",\"description\":\"12-column CSS grid layouts with varied splits create editorial magazine-style presentation that highlights featured collections.\"},{\"title\":\"Animated Mobile Navigation\",\"description\":\"Hamburger menu with staggered link animations and scroll-aware header states delivers premium mobile experience.\"},{\"title\":\"Warm Scandinavian Palette\",\"description\":\"Terracotta accents on cream backgrounds with charcoal text create a cohesive brand aesthetic that elevates artisan products.\"}],\"content\":\"$4b\",\"relativePath\":\"maison-artisan-home-lifestyle-store-template.md\"},{\"slug\":\"inspo-canvas-visual-moodboard-creator-template\",\"id\":\"inspo-canvas-visual-moodboard-creator-template\",\"title\":\"Inspo Canvas\",\"pageTitle\":\"Inspo Canvas - Visual Mood Board Creator Template\",\"category\":\"Apps\",\"project_id\":\"65195c95-fec8-4122-81a8-884673827572\",\"url\":\"https://inspo-space.lovable.app\",\"subtitle\":\"Spatial canvas for collecting, arranging, and sharing visual inspiration with drag-and-drop images, text, and AI image generation\",\"description\":\"Collect, organize, and share visual inspiration on a spatial canvas. Create mood boards with images, text, and AI-generated art — all in one beautiful workspace.\",\"metaTitle\":\"Mood Board Template | Visual Inspiration Creator | Lovable\",\"metaDescription\":\"Create and share visual mood boards with a spatial canvas. Collect images, text, and AI-generated art in one beautiful workspace - deploy in minutes.\",\"subcategory\":\"saas\",\"platform\":\"web\",\"screenshot\":\"https://storage.googleapis.com/lovable-assets/templates/inspo.jpg\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://storage.googleapis.com/lovable-assets/templates/inspo.jpg\",\"previewScreenshot\":\"https://storage.googleapis.com/lovable-assets/templates/inspo.jpg\",\"author\":{\"username\":\"Lovable\",\"avatar\":\"https://lovable.dev/img/logo/lovable-icon-bg-light.png\"},\"featured\":true,\"shownOn\":[\"homepage\",\"dashboard-templates\",\"templates\"],\"date\":\"2026-04-09T00:00:00.000000\",\"lastModified\":\"2026-04-09T00:00:00.000000\",\"highlights\":[{\"icon\":\"grid_view\",\"title\":\"Infinite spatial canvas\",\"description\":\"Place images and text anywhere on a zoomable, pannable canvas with a subtle dot grid background. No layout constraints.\"},{\"icon\":\"photo_library\",\"title\":\"Drag-and-drop image placement\",\"description\":\"Upload images from your device and place them on the canvas. Drag to reposition, resize with handles, and rotate with corner controls.\"},{\"icon\":\"auto_awesome\",\"title\":\"AI image generation\",\"description\":\"Generate images from text prompts using the built-in AI tool. Created images appear directly on your canvas ready to arrange.\"},{\"icon\":\"text_fields\",\"title\":\"Text annotations\",\"description\":\"Add text items to your canvas for notes, labels, or captions. Double-click to edit text in place.\"},{\"icon\":\"dashboard\",\"title\":\"Multiple board management\",\"description\":\"Create and manage multiple boards from a central dashboard. Each board shows a thumbnail preview, title, and last-updated timestamp.\"},{\"icon\":\"keyboard\",\"title\":\"Keyboard shortcuts and undo/redo\",\"description\":\"Full undo/redo stack and power-user shortcuts for select, copy, paste, delete, zoom, and pan.\"}],\"features\":[{\"title\":\"Infinite spatial canvas\",\"description\":\"Place images and text anywhere on a zoomable, pannable canvas with a subtle dot grid background.\"},{\"title\":\"Image upload and placement\",\"description\":\"Upload images from your device and place them on the canvas. Drag to reposition, resize with handles, and rotate with corner controls.\"},{\"title\":\"AI image generation\",\"description\":\"Generate images from text prompts using the built-in AI tool. Created images appear directly on your canvas ready to arrange.\"},{\"title\":\"Text annotations\",\"description\":\"Add text items to your canvas for notes, labels, or captions. Double-click to edit text in place.\"},{\"title\":\"Multi-board dashboard\",\"description\":\"Create and manage multiple boards from a central dashboard. Each board shows a thumbnail preview, title, and last-updated timestamp.\"},{\"title\":\"Drag-and-drop reordering\",\"description\":\"Reorder boards on the dashboard with drag-and-drop. On the canvas, freely move and arrange all items.\"},{\"title\":\"Copy and paste\",\"description\":\"Copy selected items and paste them onto the canvas. Works with keyboard shortcuts for fast workflows.\"},{\"title\":\"Undo and redo\",\"description\":\"Full undo/redo stack for canvas actions. Never worry about losing work from an accidental move or delete.\"},{\"title\":\"Context menu\",\"description\":\"Right-click any item for quick actions — copy, paste, delete, and more.\"},{\"title\":\"Floating toolbar\",\"description\":\"A dock at the bottom of the canvas gives you quick access to tools — select, upload, text, delete, download, and AI generate.\"},{\"title\":\"Keyboard shortcuts\",\"description\":\"Power-user shortcuts for select, copy, paste, undo, delete, zoom, and pan. A built-in shortcuts panel shows all available keys.\"},{\"title\":\"Board export\",\"description\":\"Download your canvas as an image to share or use in presentations.\"},{\"title\":\"Authentication\",\"description\":\"Email-based signup and login with Google sign-in support. Users verify their email before accessing the app.\"},{\"title\":\"Responsive design\",\"description\":\"Works on desktop and adapts to different screen sizes with a responsive canvas and UI.\"},{\"title\":\"Dark and light mode\",\"description\":\"Toggle between dark and light themes from the dashboard navbar.\"}],\"content\":\"$4c\",\"relativePath\":\"inspo-canvas-visual-moodboard-creator-template.md\"},{\"slug\":\"perspective-lifestyle\",\"id\":\"7410f81b-8218-4f2d-bb32-1ba1f84eabb2\",\"title\":\"Personal blog\",\"pageTitle\":\"Perspective - Lifestyle Blog Template\",\"category\":\"Websites\",\"project_id\":\"af765f7c-2a17-4308-8692-b32f9c93f440\",\"url\":\"https://my-perspective-lifestyle.lovable.app/\",\"subtitle\":\"A sophisticated lifestyle blog template designed for wellness, travel, and personal growth content.\",\"tagline\":\"Muted, intimate design\",\"description\":\"A sophisticated lifestyle blog template designed for wellness, travel, and personal growth content. Features elegant layouts, inspiring design, and comprehensive content organization perfect for lifestyle influencers and educators.\",\"metaTitle\":\"Lifestyle Blog Template | Wellness \u0026 Travel | Lovable\",\"metaDescription\":\"A professional lifestyle blog template covering wellness, travel, and personal growth. Built with React and Tailwind - ready to customise and publish.\",\"subcategory\":\"blog\",\"platform\":\"Web\",\"tags\":[\"Blog\",\"Lifestyle\",\"Wellness\",\"Travel\",\"Personal Growth\",\"Content\"],\"screenshot\":\"https://pub-bb2e103a32db4e198524a2e9ed8f35b4.r2.dev/a8b116a9-20b6-43a8-ae91-693ba5a35c3b/id-preview-172571d0--7410f81b-8218-4f2d-bb32-1ba1f84eabb2.lovable.app-1760028648399.png\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://pub-bb2e103a32db4e198524a2e9ed8f35b4.r2.dev/a8b116a9-20b6-43a8-ae91-693ba5a35c3b/id-preview-172571d0--7410f81b-8218-4f2d-bb32-1ba1f84eabb2.lovable.app-1760028648399.png\",\"previewScreenshot\":\"https://assets.lovable.dev/templates/previews/perspective-lifestyle-preview.webp\",\"colorPalette\":[\"#F5F1E8\",\"#3D3D3D\",\"#6B7280\",\"#4A3728\",\"#FAFAFA\"],\"author\":{\"username\":\"Lovable\",\"avatar\":\"https://lovable.dev/img/logo/lovable-icon-bg-light.png\"},\"shownOn\":[\"homepage\",\"templates\"],\"is_partner_template\":false,\"date\":\"2025-10-09T10:00:00.000Z\",\"highlights\":[{\"icon\":\"stars\",\"title\":\"Editorial-Grade Design System\",\"description\":\"Premium typography and warm aesthetic optimized for content-focused blogs and publications\"},{\"icon\":\"newspaper\",\"title\":\"Content-First Architecture\",\"description\":\"Multi-section articles with categories, tags, and related content for superior discoverability\"},{\"icon\":\"half_moon\",\"title\":\"Built-in Dark Mode\",\"description\":\"Complete light and dark theme system with automatic detection and preference persistence\"},{\"icon\":\"gauge\",\"title\":\"Lightning-Fast Performance\",\"description\":\"Vite-powered development with optimized builds, tree-shaking, and GPU-accelerated animations for sub-2s loads\"},{\"icon\":\"phone_iphone\",\"title\":\"Mobile-First Responsive Design\",\"description\":\"Touch-optimized interactions and adaptive layouts across all devices from phones to desktops\"},{\"icon\":\"search\",\"title\":\"SEO \u0026 Accessibility Ready\",\"description\":\"WCAG AAA contrast ratios, semantic markup, and complete meta tag structure for discoverability\"}],\"features\":[{\"title\":\"Sophisticated Typography Hierarchy\",\"description\":\"Premium Google Fonts pairing of Inter and Merriweather with fluid responsive scaling for exceptional readability across all screen sizes\"},{\"title\":\"Category-Based Content Organization\",\"description\":\"Seven semantic categories with unique color coding, dedicated landing pages, and intelligent filtering for intuitive content discovery and navigation\"},{\"title\":\"Advanced Card Hover Effects\",\"description\":\"Dual-shadow elevation system with scale transforms and image zoom effects creating engaging, modern interactions that guide user attention\"},{\"title\":\"Related Content Engine\",\"description\":\"Automatic category-based article recommendations displayed in three-column grids to increase time-on-site and reduce bounce rates significantly\"},{\"title\":\"Social Sharing Integration\",\"description\":\"Platform-optimized share buttons for Twitter, Facebook, and LinkedIn with copy-link functionality and toast notifications for seamless content distribution\"},{\"title\":\"Newsletter Subscription Forms\",\"description\":\"Multiple strategically-placed email capture CTAs with rounded-full styling, ready for Mailchimp or ConvertKit integration to grow subscriber lists\"},{\"title\":\"TypeScript Full-Stack Foundation\",\"description\":\"Type-safe React components with strict interfaces and path aliases enabling confident refactoring, easy maintenance, and seamless CMS integration\"},{\"title\":\"Customizable Design Tokens\",\"description\":\"CSS variable-based color system and spacing scale allowing instant brand customization without touching component code or complex configurations\"},{\"title\":\"Author Attribution System\",\"description\":\"Rich author profiles with avatars and bios, creating credibility and personality while supporting multiple contributors for growing editorial teams\"},{\"title\":\"Glassmorphism UI Elements\",\"description\":\"Backdrop-blur floating buttons and semi-transparent overlays adding sophisticated depth and modern polish to category badges and navigation pills\"},{\"title\":\"Staggered Entry Animations\",\"description\":\"Progressive reveal animations with customizable delays creating cinematic page loads that feel premium and guide attention through content hierarchy\"},{\"title\":\"Production-Ready Deployment\",\"description\":\"Optimized Vite build pipeline with automatic code splitting, CSS purging, and static output ready for Vercel, Netlify, or any CDN\"}],\"version\":2,\"stylePackVariants\":{\"Neutral\":\"cf130624-6a88-446e-9ac7-fc1e9cbce027\",\"Warm\":\"88794be6-170a-473f-af77-9ee4e6fa81a6\",\"Quirky\":\"0bf4d1c9-a9a0-42e7-b0e8-b3cdeff0ee6e\",\"Dark\":\"be3642ae-98c0-4fe4-b9b6-170f8a39ca53\",\"Red Velvet\":\"2cde2056-5a9e-45a9-9369-3e6665678faa\"},\"designedFor\":[\"Writers and journalists building independent publications\",\"Industry experts sharing insights and analysis\",\"Creators monetizing through subscriptions and sponsorships\",\"Thought leaders establishing authority in their field\"],\"techStack\":[\"React\",\"TypeScript\",\"Tailwind CSS\",\"Vite\",\"TanStack Query\",\"shadcn/ui\",\"Radix UI\",\"Lucide Icons\"],\"content\":\"$4d\",\"relativeP