animations, static data architecture, and minimal JavaScript for sub-2s load times\"},{\"icon\":\"phone_iphone\",\"title\":\"Mobile-First Responsive Layout\",\"description\":\"Adaptive grid system transforming 1 to 3 columns with immersive edge-to-edge mobile experience\"},{\"icon\":\"accessibility\",\"title\":\"Built for Accessibility\",\"description\":\"Semantic HTML, AAA contrast ratios, keyboard navigation, and screen reader optimized structure\"},{\"icon\":\"search\",\"title\":\"SEO-Ready Architecture\",\"description\":\"Prepared for dynamic meta tags, structured data, and social sharing optimization capabilities\"},{\"icon\":\"code\",\"title\":\"Extensible Modern Stack\",\"description\":\"React 18, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS with Lovable Cloud integration ready for scaling\"}],\"features\":[{\"title\":\"Vibrant Color System\",\"description\":\"Eight distinct card colors with warm cream background and pure black typography.\"},{\"title\":\"Premium Typography\",\"description\":\"Lora serif body text and Supreme sans-serif headings with responsive scaling.\"},{\"title\":\"Interactive Article Cards\",\"description\":\"Hover effects with grayscale-to-color transitions and consistent grid layouts.\"},{\"title\":\"Featured Content Display\",\"description\":\"Hero split layout with prominent call-to-action for editorial curation.\"},{\"title\":\"Newsletter Integration\",\"description\":\"Email capture with validation, async submission, and toast notifications.\"},{\"title\":\"Progressive Loading\",\"description\":\"Load-more pagination starting at 6 articles, maintaining scroll position.\"},{\"title\":\"Related Articles\",\"description\":\"Contextual recommendations on article pages to drive deeper engagement.\"},{\"title\":\"Dark Mode Ready\",\"description\":\"CSS variable system with inverted scheme defined, ready for one-click activation.\"},{\"title\":\"CMS Ready\",\"description\":\"Prepared for Supabase or headless CMS integration with React Query.\"},{\"title\":\"Optimized Images\",\"description\":\"CDN integration with automatic compression and layout-shift prevention.\"},{\"title\":\"Production Codebase\",\"description\":\"TypeScript strict mode, Vite with SWC, path aliases, and ESLint configured.\"},{\"title\":\"Social Sharing\",\"description\":\"Open Graph and Twitter Card meta tags with pre-configured social images.\"}],\"version\":2,\"stylePackVariants\":{\"Neutral\":\"aeaaa038-f050-4f57-b03d-7b80213d6df4\",\"Warm\":\"b788c325-6d17-4046-baa5-e9f380651e61\",\"Quirky\":\"08af2833-f2c5-48b3-b41d-b9060eee2c96\",\"Dark\":\"1137c063-3de4-48b0-9051-bb0898b8b90e\",\"Red Velvet\":\"dffa3515-3b90-4d8e-b773-e76b978f047a\"},\"designedFor\":[\"Fashion bloggers building a personal brand\",\"Style influencers creating lookbooks and outfit posts\",\"Personal stylists showcasing client work\",\"Boutique owners combining blog content with products\"],\"techStack\":[\"React\",\"TypeScript\",\"Tailwind CSS\",\"Vite\",\"TanStack Query\",\"shadcn/ui\",\"Radix UI\",\"Lucide Icons\"],\"content\":\"$4e\",\"relativePath\":\"vesper.md\",\"stylePacks\":[{\"label\":\"Neutral\",\"previewColor\":\"#2c3138\",\"colors\":[\"#2c3138\",\"#E2E6EA\",\"#F2F5F7\",\"#2c3138\"],\"colorTokens\":{\"primary\":\"oklch(35% 0 0)\",\"primaryForeground\":\"oklch(97% 0 0)\",\"background\":\"oklch(98% 0 0)\",\"foreground\":\"oklch(30% 0 0)\",\"secondary\":\"oklch(92% 0 0)\",\"secondaryForeground\":\"oklch(30% 0 0)\",\"accent\":\"oklch(90% 0 0)\",\"accentForeground\":\"oklch(30% 0 0)\",\"muted\":\"oklch(88% 0 0)\",\"mutedForeground\":\"oklch(50% 0 0)\",\"card\":\"oklch(94% 0 0)\",\"cardForeground\":\"oklch(30% 0 0)\",\"popover\":\"oklch(94% 0 0)\",\"popoverForeground\":\"oklch(30% 0 0)\",\"destructive\":\"oklch(62.8% 0.208 22.7)\",\"destructiveForeground\":\"oklch(100% 0 0)\",\"border\":\"oklch(85% 0 0)\",\"input\":\"oklch(85% 0 0)\",\"ring\":\"oklch(30% 0 0)\"},\"font\":{\"heading\":{\"family\":\"Geist\",\"url\":\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Geist:wght@400;